<p id="fs-id1165042364649">You need to construct a fence around an area of <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mn>1600</mn><mspace width="0.2em"/><mtext>ft</mtext><mo>.</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mn>1600</mn><mspace width="0.2em"/><mtext>ft</mtext><mo>.</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> What are the dimensions of the rectangular pen to minimize the amount of material needed?</p>
