<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1165042331767">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1165042331769">
<p id="fs-id1165042331771">Find a function that measures the total amount of time it takes to reach the drowning person as a function of the swim angle, <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>&#952;</mi><mo>.</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>&#952;</mi><mo>.</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
