<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1165042472042">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1165042472044">
<p id="fs-id1165042472046">Find at what angle <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mi>&#952;</mi></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mi>&#952;</mi></annotation-xml></semantics></math> the lifeguard should swim to reach the drowning person in the least amount of time.</p>
