<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1165042369580">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1165042369582">
<p id="fs-id1165042369584">A truck uses gas as <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>v</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>v</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi>b</mi><mi>v</mi></mfrac><mo>,</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>g</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>v</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>v</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mi>b</mi><mi>v</mi></mfrac><mo>,</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> where <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mi>v</mi></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mi>v</mi></annotation-xml></semantics></math> represents the speed of the truck and <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mi>g</mi></annotation-xml></semantics></math> represents the gallons of fuel per mile. At what speed is fuel consumption minimized?</p>
</div>
<div data-type="solution" id="fs-id1165042374583">
<p id="fs-id1165042374585"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mrow><mfrac><mi>b</mi><mi>a</mi></mfrac></mrow></msqrt></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mrow><mfrac><mi>b</mi><mi>a</mi></mfrac></mrow></msqrt></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
