<p id="fs-id1165043430975"><strong data-effect="bold">[T]</strong> Where is the parabola <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> closest to point <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>?</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>?</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
</div>
